(4076, 'who was faithful to Him who appointed Him, as Moses also was faithful in all His house.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 558, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4077, 'For this One has been counted worthy of more glory than Moses, inasmuch as He who built the house has more honor than the house.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 559, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4078, 'For every house is built by someone, but He who built all things is God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 560, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4079, 'And Moses indeed was faithful in all His house as a servant, for a testimony of those things which would be spoken afterward,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 561, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4080, 'but Christ as a Son over His own house, whose house we are if we hold fast the confidence and the rejoicing of the hope firm to the end.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 562, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4081, 'Therefore, as the Holy Spirit says: \"Today, if you will hear His voice,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 563, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4082, 'Do not harden your hearts as in the rebellion, In the day of trial in the wilderness,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 564, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4083, 'Where your fathers tested Me, tried Me, And saw My works forty years.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 565, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4084, 'Therefore I was angry with that generation, And said, \'They always go astray in their heart, And they have not known My ways.\'', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 566, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4085, 'So I swore in My wrath, \'They shall not enter My rest.\' \"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 567, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4086, 'Beware, brethren, lest there be in any of you an evil heart of unbelief in departing from the living God;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 568, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4087, 'but exhort one another daily, while it is called \"Today,\" lest any of you be hardened through the deceitfulness of sin.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 569, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4088, 'For we have become partakers of Christ if we hold the beginning of our confidence steadfast to the end,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 570, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4089, 'while it is said: \"Today, if you will hear His voice, Do not harden your hearts as in the rebellion.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 571, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4090, 'For who, having heard, rebelled? Indeed, was it not all who came out of Egypt, led by Moses?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 572, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4091, 'Now with whom was He angry forty years? Was it not with those who sinned, whose corpses fell in the wilderness?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 573, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4092, 'And to whom did He swear that they would not enter His rest, but to those who did not obey?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 574, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4093, 'So we see that they could not enter in because of unbelief.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 575, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4094, 'Therefore, since a promise remains of entering His rest, let us fear lest any of you seem to have come short of it.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 576, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4095, 'For indeed the gospel was preached to us as well as to them; but the word which they heard did not profit them, not being mixed with faith in those who heard it.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 577, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4096, 'For we who have believed do enter that rest, as He has said: \"So I swore in My wrath, \'They shall not enter My rest,\' \" although the works were finished from the foundation of the world.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 578, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4097, 'For He has spoken in a certain place of the seventh day in this way: \"And God rested on the seventh day from all His works\";', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 579, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4098, 'and again in this place: \"They shall not enter My rest.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 580, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4099, 'Since therefore it remains that some must enter it, and those to whom it was first preached did not enter because of disobedience,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 581, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4100, 'again He designates a certain day, saying in David, \"Today,\" after such a long time, as it has been said: \"Today, if you will hear His voice, Do not harden your hearts.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 582, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4101, 'For if Joshua had given them rest, then He would not afterward have spoken of another day.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 583, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4102, 'There remains therefore a rest for the people of God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 584, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4103, 'For he who has entered His rest has himself also ceased from his works as God did from His.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 585, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4104, 'Let us therefore be diligent to enter that rest, lest anyone fall according to the same example of disobedience.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 586, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4105, 'For the word of God is living and powerful, and sharper than any two-edged sword, piercing even to the division of soul and spirit, and of joints and marrow, and is a discerner of the thoughts and intents of the heart.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 587, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4106, 'And there is no creature hidden from His sight, but all things are naked and open to the eyes of Him to whom we must give account.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 588, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4107, 'Seeing then that we have a great High Priest who has passed through the heavens, Jesus the Son of God, let us hold fast our confession.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 589, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4108, 'For we do not have a High Priest who cannot sympathize with our weaknesses, but was in all points tempted as we are, yet without sin.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 590, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4109, 'Let us therefore come boldly to the throne of grace, that we may obtain mercy and find grace to help in time of need.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 591, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4110, 'For every high priest taken from among men is appointed for men in things pertaining to God, that he may offer both gifts and sacrifices for sins.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 592, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4111, 'He can have compassion on those who are ignorant and going astray, since he himself is also subject to weakness.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 593, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4112, 'Because of this he is required as for the people, so also for himself, to offer sacrifices for sins.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 594, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4113, 'And no man takes this honor to himself, but he who is called by God, just as Aaron was.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 595, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4114, 'So also Christ did not glorify Himself to become High Priest, but it was He who said to Him: \"You are My Son, Today I have begotten You.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 596, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4115, 'As He also says in another place: \"You are a priest forever According to the order of Melchizedek\";', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 597, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4116, 'who, in the days of His flesh, when He had offered up prayers and supplications, with vehement cries and tears to Him who was able to save Him from death, and was heard because of His godly fear,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 598, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4117, 'though He was a Son, yet He learned obedience by the things which He suffered.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 599, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4118, 'And having been perfected, He became the author of eternal salvation to all who obey Him,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 600, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4119, 'called by God as High Priest \"according to the order of Melchizedek,\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 601, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4120, 'of whom we have much to say, and hard to explain, since you have become dull of hearing.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 602, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4121, 'For though by this time you ought to be teachers, you need someone to teach you again the first principles of the oracles of God; and you have come to need milk and not solid food.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 603, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4122, 'For everyone who partakes only of milk is unskilled in the word of righteousness, for he is a babe.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 604, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4123, 'But solid food belongs to those who are of full age, that is, those who by reason of use have their senses exercised to discern both good and evil.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 605, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4124, 'Therefore, leaving the discussion of the elementary principles of Christ, let us go on to perfection, not laying again the foundation of repentance from dead works and of faith toward God,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 606, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4125, 'of the doctrine of baptisms, of laying on of hands, of resurrection of the dead, and of eternal judgment.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 607, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4126, 'And this we will do if God permits.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 608, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4127, 'For it is impossible for those who were once enlightened, and have tasted the heavenly gift, and have become partakers of the Holy Spirit,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 609, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4128, 'and have tasted the good word of God and the powers of the age to come,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 610, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4129, 'if they fall away, to renew them again to repentance, since they crucify again for themselves the Son of God, and put Him to an open shame.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 611, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4130, 'For the earth which drinks in the rain that often comes upon it, and bears herbs useful for those by whom it is cultivated, receives blessing from God;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 612, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4131, 'but if it bears thorns and briers, it is rejected and near to being cursed, whose end is to be burned.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 613, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4132, 'But, beloved, we are confident of better things concerning you, yes, things that accompany salvation, though we speak in this manner.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 614, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4133, 'For God is not unjust to forget your work and labor of love which you have shown toward His name, in that you have ministered to the saints, and do minister.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 615, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4134, 'And we desire that each one of you show the same diligence to the full assurance of hope until the end,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 616, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4135, 'that you do not become sluggish, but imitate those who through faith and patience inherit the promises.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 617, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4136, 'For when God made a promise to Abraham, because He could swear by no one greater, He swore by Himself,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 618, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4137, 'saying, \"Surely blessing I will bless you, and multiplying I will multiply you.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 619, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4138, 'And so, after he had patiently endured, he obtained the promise.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 620, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4139, 'For men indeed swear by the greater, and an oath for confirmation is for them an end of all dispute.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 621, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4140, 'Thus God, determining to show more abundantly to the heirs of promise the immutability of His counsel, confirmed it by an oath,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 622, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4141, 'that by two immutable things, in which it is impossible for God to lie, we might have strong consolation, who have fled for refuge to lay hold of the hope set before us.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 623, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4142, 'This hope we have as an anchor of the soul, both sure and steadfast, and which enters the Presence behind the veil,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 624, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4143, 'where the forerunner has entered for us, even Jesus, having become High Priest forever according to the order of Melchizedek.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 625, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4144, 'For this Melchizedek, king of Salem, priest of the Most High God, who met Abraham returning from the slaughter of the kings and blessed him,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 626, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4145, 'to whom also Abraham gave a tenth part of all, first being translated \"king of righteousness,\" and then also king of Salem, meaning \"king of peace,\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 627, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4146, 'without father, without mother, without genealogy, having neither beginning of days nor end of life, but made like the Son of God, remains a priest continually.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 628, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4147, 'Now consider how great this man was, to whom even the patriarch Abraham gave a tenth of the spoils.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 629, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4148, 'And indeed those who are of the sons of Levi, who receive the priesthood, have a commandment to receive tithes from the people according to the law, that is, from their brethren, though they have come from the loins of Abraham;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 630, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4149, 'but he whose genealogy is not derived from them received tithes from Abraham and blessed him who had the promises.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 631, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4150, 'Now beyond all contradiction the lesser is blessed by the better.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 632, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4151, 'Here mortal men receive tithes, but there he receives them, of whom it is witnessed that he lives.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 633, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4152, 'Even Levi, who receives tithes, paid tithes through Abraham, so to speak,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 634, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4153, 'for he was still in the loins of his father when Melchizedek met him.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 635, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4154, 'Therefore, if perfection were through the Levitical priesthood (for under it the people received the law), what further need was there that another priest should rise according to the order of Melchizedek, and not be called according to the order of Aaron?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 636, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4155, 'For the priesthood being changed, of necessity there is also a change of the law.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 637, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4156, 'For He of whom these things are spoken belongs to another tribe, from which no man has officiated at the altar.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 638, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4157, 'For it is evident that our Lord arose from Judah, of which tribe Moses spoke nothing concerning priesthood.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 639, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4158, 'And it is yet far more evident if, in the likeness of Melchizedek, there arises another priest', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 640, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4159, 'who has come, not according to the law of a fleshly commandment, but according to the power of an endless life.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 641, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4160, 'For He testifies: \"You are a priest forever According to the order of Melchizedek.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 642, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4161, 'For on the one hand there is an annulling of the former commandment because of its weakness and unprofitableness,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 643, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4162, 'for the law made nothing perfect; on the other hand, there is the bringing in of a better hope, through which we draw near to God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 644, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4163, 'And inasmuch as He was not made priest without an oath', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 645, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4164, '(for they have become priests without an oath, but He with an oath by Him who said to Him: \"The Lord has sworn And will not relent, \'You are a priest forever According to the order of Melchizedek\' \"),', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 646, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4165, 'by so much more Jesus has become a surety of a better covenant.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 647, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4166, 'Also there were many priests, because they were prevented by death from continuing.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 648, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4167, 'But He, because He continues forever, has an unchangeable priesthood.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 649, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4168, 'Therefore He is also able to save to the uttermost those who come to God through Him, since He always lives to make intercession for them.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 650, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4169, 'For such a High Priest was fitting for us, who is holy, harmless, undefiled, separate from sinners, and has become higher than the heavens;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 651, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4170, 'who does not need daily, as those high priests, to offer up sacrifices, first for His own sins and then for the people\'s, for this He did once for all when He offered up Himself.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 652, NULL, NULL, 1);
INSERT INTO `Questions` (`QuestionID`, `Question`, `Answer`, `NumberPoints`, `DateCreated`, `DateModified`, `Type`, `CommentaryStartPage`, `CommentaryEndPage`, `IsDeleted`, `CreatorID`, `LastEditedByID`, `StartVerseID`, `EndVerseID`, `CommentaryID`, `LanguageID`) VALUES
(4171, 'For the law appoints as high priests men who have weakness, but the word of the oath, which came after the law, appoints the Son who has been perfected forever.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 653, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4172, 'Now this is the main point of the things we are saying: We have such a High Priest, who is seated at the right hand of the throne of the Majesty in the heavens,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 654, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4173, 'a Minister of the sanctuary and of the true tabernacle which the Lord erected, and not man.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 655, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4174, 'For every high priest is appointed to offer both gifts and sacrifices. Therefore it is necessary that this One also have something to offer.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 656, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4175, 'For if He were on earth, He would not be a priest, since there are priests who offer the gifts according to the law;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 657, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4176, 'who serve the copy and shadow of the heavenly things, as Moses was divinely instructed when he was about to make the tabernacle. For He said, \"See that you make all things according to the pattern shown you on the mountain.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 658, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4177, 'But now He has obtained a more excellent ministry, inasmuch as He is also Mediator of a better covenant, which was established on better promises.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 659, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4178, 'For if that first covenant had been faultless, then no place would have been sought for a second.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 660, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4179, 'Because finding fault with them, He says: \"Behold, the days are coming, says the Lord, when I will make a new covenant with the house of Israel and with the house of Judah--', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 661, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4180, 'not according to the covenant that I made with their fathers in the day when I took them by the hand to lead them out of the land of Egypt; because they did not continue in My covenant, and I disregarded them, says the Lord.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 662, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4181, 'For this is the covenant that I will make with the house of Israel after those days, says the Lord: I will put My laws in their mind and write them on their hearts; and I will be their God, and they shall be My people.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 663, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4182, 'None of them shall teach his neighbor, and none his brother, saying, \'Know the Lord,\' for all shall know Me, from the least of them to the greatest of them.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 664, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4183, 'For I will be merciful to their unrighteousness, and their sins and their lawless deeds I will remember no more.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 665, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4184, 'In that He says, \"A new covenant,\" He has made the first obsolete. Now what is becoming obsolete and growing old is ready to vanish away.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 666, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4185, 'Then indeed, even the first covenant had ordinances of divine service and the earthly sanctuary.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:37', '2020-11-23 00:21:37', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 667, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4186, 'For a tabernacle was prepared: the first part, in which was the lampstand, the table, and the showbread, which is called the sanctuary;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 668, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4187, 'and behind the second veil, the part of the tabernacle which is called the Holiest of All,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 669, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4188, 'which had the golden censer and the ark of the covenant overlaid on all sides with gold, in which were the golden pot that had the manna, Aaron\'s rod that budded, and the tablets of the covenant;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 670, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4189, 'and above it were the cherubim of glory overshadowing the mercy seat. Of these things we cannot now speak in detail.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 671, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4190, 'Now when these things had been thus prepared, the priests always went into the first part of the tabernacle, performing the services.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 672, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4191, 'But into the second part the high priest went alone once a year, not without blood, which he offered for himself and for the people\'s sins committed in ignorance;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 673, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4192, 'the Holy Spirit indicating this, that the way into the Holiest of All was not yet made manifest while the first tabernacle was still standing.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 674, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4193, 'It was symbolic for the present time in which both gifts and sacrifices are offered which cannot make him who performed the service perfect in regard to the conscience--', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 675, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4194, 'concerned only with foods and drinks, various washings, and fleshly ordinances imposed until the time of reformation.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 676, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4195, 'But Christ came as High Priest of the good things to come, with the greater and more perfect tabernacle not made with hands, that is, not of this creation.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 677, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4196, 'Not with the blood of goats and calves, but with His own blood He entered the Most Holy Place once for all, having obtained eternal redemption.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 678, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4197, 'For if the blood of bulls and goats and the ashes of a heifer, sprinkling the unclean, sanctifies for the purifying of the flesh,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 679, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4198, 'how much more shall the blood of Christ, who through the eternal Spirit offered Himself without spot to God, cleanse your conscience from dead works to serve the living God?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 680, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4199, 'And for this reason He is the Mediator of the new covenant, by means of death, for the redemption of the transgressions under the first covenant, that those who are called may receive the promise of the eternal inheritance.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 681, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4200, 'For where there is a testament, there must also of necessity be the death of the testator.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 682, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4201, 'For a testament is in force after men are dead, since it has no power at all while the testator lives.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 683, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4202, 'Therefore not even the first covenant was dedicated without blood.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 684, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4203, 'For when Moses had spoken every precept to all the people according to the law, he took the blood of calves and goats, with water, scarlet wool, and hyssop, and sprinkled both the book itself and all the people,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 685, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4204, 'saying, \"This is the blood of the covenant which God has commanded you.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 686, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4205, 'Then likewise he sprinkled with blood both the tabernacle and all the vessels of the ministry.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 687, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4206, 'And according to the law almost all things are purified with blood, and without shedding of blood there is no remission.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 688, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4207, 'Therefore it was necessary that the copies of the things in the heavens should be purified with these, but the heavenly things themselves with better sacrifices than these.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 689, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4208, 'For Christ has not entered the holy places made with hands, which are copies of the true, but into heaven itself, now to appear in the presence of God for us;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 690, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4209, 'not that He should offer Himself often, as the high priest enters the Most Holy Place every year with blood of another--', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 691, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4210, 'He then would have had to suffer often since the foundation of the world; but now, once at the end of the ages, He has appeared to put away sin by the sacrifice of Himself.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 692, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4211, 'And as it is appointed for men to die once, but after this the judgment,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 693, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4212, 'so Christ was offered once to bear the sins of many. To those who eagerly wait for Him He will appear a second time, apart from sin, for salvation.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 694, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4213, 'For the law, having a shadow of the good things to come, and not the very image of the things, can never with these same sacrifices, which they offer continually year by year, make those who approach perfect.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 695, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4214, 'For then would they not have ceased to be offered? For the worshipers, once purified, would have had no more consciousness of sins.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 696, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4215, 'But in those sacrifices there is a reminder of sins every year.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 697, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4216, 'For it is not possible that the blood of bulls and goats could take away sins.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 698, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4217, 'Therefore, when He came into the world, He said: \"Sacrifice and offering You did not desire, But a body You have prepared for Me.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 699, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4218, 'In burnt offerings and sacrifices for sin You had no pleasure.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 700, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4219, 'Then I said, \'Behold, I have come--In the volume of the book it is written of Me--To do Your will, O God.\' \"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 701, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4220, 'Previously saying, \"Sacrifice and offering, burnt offerings, and offerings for sin You did not desire, nor had pleasure in them \" (which are offered according to the law),', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 702, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4221, 'then He said, \"Behold, I have come to do Your will, O God.\" He takes away the first that He may establish the second.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 703, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4222, 'By that will we have been sanctified through the offering of the body of Jesus Christ once for all.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 704, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4223, 'And every priest stands ministering daily and offering repeatedly the same sacrifices, which can never take away sins.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 705, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4224, 'But this Man, after He had offered one sacrifice for sins forever, sat down at the right hand of God,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 706, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4225, 'from that time waiting till His enemies are made His footstool.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 707, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4226, 'For by one offering He has perfected forever those who are being sanctified.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 708, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4227, 'But the Holy Spirit also witnesses to us; for after He had said before,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 709, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4228, '\"This is the covenant that I will make with them after those days, says the Lord: I will put My laws into their hearts, and in their minds I will write them,\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 710, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4229, 'then He adds, \"Their sins and their lawless deeds I will remember no more.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 711, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4230, 'Now where there is remission of these, there is no longer an offering for sin.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 712, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4231, 'Therefore, brethren, having boldness to enter the Holiest by the blood of Jesus,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 713, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4232, 'by a new and living way which He consecrated for us, through the veil, that is, His flesh,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 714, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4233, 'and having a High Priest over the house of God,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 715, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4234, 'let us draw near with a true heart in full assurance of faith, having our hearts sprinkled from an evil conscience and our bodies washed with pure water.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 716, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4235, 'Let us hold fast the confession of our hope without wavering, for He who promised is faithful.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 717, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4236, 'And let us consider one another in order to stir up love and good works,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 718, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4237, 'not forsaking the assembling of ourselves together, as is the manner of some, but exhorting one another, and so much the more as you see the Day approaching.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 719, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4238, 'For if we sin willfully after we have received the knowledge of the truth, there no longer remains a sacrifice for sins,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 720, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4239, 'but a certain fearful expectation of judgment, and fiery indignation which will devour the adversaries.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 721, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4240, 'Anyone who has rejected Moses\' law dies without mercy on the testimony of two or three witnesses.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 722, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4241, 'Of how much worse punishment, do you suppose, will he be thought worthy who has trampled the Son of God underfoot, counted the blood of the covenant by which he was sanctified a common thing, and insulted the Spirit of grace?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 723, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4242, 'For we know Him who said, \"Vengeance is Mine, I will repay,\" says the Lord. And again, \"The Lord will judge His people.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 724, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4243, 'It is a fearful thing to fall into the hands of the living God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 725, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4244, 'But recall the former days in which, after you were illuminated, you endured a great struggle with sufferings:', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 726, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4245, 'partly while you were made a spectacle both by reproaches and tribulations, and partly while you became companions of those who were so treated;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 727, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4246, 'for you had compassion on me in my chains, and joyfully accepted the plundering of your goods, knowing that you have a better and an enduring possession for yourselves in heaven.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 728, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4247, 'Therefore do not cast away your confidence, which has great reward.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 729, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4248, 'For you have need of endurance, so that after you have done the will of God, you may receive the promise:', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 730, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4249, '\"For yet a little while, And He who is coming will come and will not tarry.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 731, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4250, 'Now the just shall live by faith; But if anyone draws back, My soul has no pleasure in him.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 732, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4251, 'But we are not of those who draw back to perdition, but of those who believe to the saving of the soul.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 733, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4252, 'Now faith is the substance of things hoped for, the evidence of things not seen.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 734, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4253, 'For by it the elders obtained a good testimony.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 735, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4254, 'By faith we understand that the worlds were framed by the word of God, so that the things which are seen were not made of things which are visible.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 736, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4255, 'By faith Abel offered to God a more excellent sacrifice than Cain, through which he obtained witness that he was righteous, God testifying of his gifts; and through it he being dead still speaks.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 737, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4256, 'By faith Enoch was taken away so that he did not see death, \"and was not found, because God had taken him\"; for before he was taken he had this testimony, that he pleased God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 738, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4257, 'But without faith it is impossible to please Him, for he who comes to God must believe that He is, and that He is a rewarder of those who diligently seek Him.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 739, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4258, 'By faith Noah, being divinely warned of things not yet seen, moved with godly fear, prepared an ark for the saving of his household, by which he condemned the world and became heir of the righteousness which is according to faith.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 740, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4259, 'By faith Abraham obeyed when he was called to go out to the place which he would receive as an inheritance. And he went out, not knowing where he was going.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 741, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4260, 'By faith he dwelt in the land of promise as in a foreign country, dwelling in tents with Isaac and Jacob, the heirs with him of the same promise;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 742, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4261, 'for he waited for the city which has foundations, whose builder and maker is God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 743, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4262, 'By faith Sarah herself also received strength to conceive seed, and she bore a child when she was past the age, because she judged Him faithful who had promised.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 744, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4263, 'Therefore from one man, and him as good as dead, were born as many as the stars of the sky in multitude--innumerable as the sand which is by the seashore.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 745, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4264, 'These all died in faith, not having received the promises, but having seen them afar off were assured of them, embraced them and confessed that they were strangers and pilgrims on the earth.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 746, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4265, 'For those who say such things declare plainly that they seek a homeland.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 747, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4266, 'And truly if they had called to mind that country from which they had come out, they would have had opportunity to return.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 748, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4267, 'But now they desire a better, that is, a heavenly country. Therefore God is not ashamed to be called their God, for He has prepared a city for them.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 749, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4268, 'By faith Abraham, when he was tested, offered up Isaac, and he who had received the promises offered up his only begotten son,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 750, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4269, 'of whom it was said, \"In Isaac your seed shall be called,\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 751, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4270, 'concluding that God was able to raise him up, even from the dead, from which he also received him in a figurative sense.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 752, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4271, 'By faith Isaac blessed Jacob and Esau concerning things to come.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 753, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4272, 'By faith Jacob, when he was dying, blessed each of the sons of Joseph, and worshiped, leaning on the top of his staff.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 754, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4273, 'By faith Joseph, when he was dying, made mention of the departure of the children of Israel, and gave instructions concerning his bones.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 755, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4274, 'By faith Moses, when he was born, was hidden three months by his parents, because they saw he was a beautiful child; and they were not afraid of the king\'s command.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 756, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4275, 'By faith Moses, when he became of age, refused to be called the son of Pharaoh\'s daughter,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 757, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4276, 'choosing rather to suffer affliction with the people of God than to enjoy the passing pleasures of sin,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 758, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4277, 'esteeming the reproach of Christ greater riches than the treasures in Egypt; for he looked to the reward.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 759, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4278, 'By faith he forsook Egypt, not fearing the wrath of the king; for he endured as seeing Him who is invisible.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 760, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4279, 'By faith he kept the Passover and the sprinkling of blood, lest he who destroyed the firstborn should touch them.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 761, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4280, 'By faith they passed through the Red Sea as by dry land, whereas the Egyptians, attempting to do so, were drowned.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 762, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4281, 'By faith the walls of Jericho fell down after they were encircled for seven days.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 763, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4282, 'By faith the harlot Rahab did not perish with those who did not believe, when she had received the spies with peace.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 764, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4283, 'And what more shall I say? For the time would fail me to tell of Gideon and Barak and Samson and Jephthah, also of David and Samuel and the prophets:', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 765, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4284, 'who through faith subdued kingdoms, worked righteousness, obtained promises, stopped the mouths of lions,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 766, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4285, 'quenched the violence of fire, escaped the edge of the sword, out of weakness were made strong, became valiant in battle, turned to flight the armies of the aliens.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 767, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4286, 'Women received their dead raised to life again. Others were tortured, not accepting deliverance, that they might obtain a better resurrection.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 768, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4287, 'Still others had trial of mockings and scourgings, yes, and of chains and imprisonment.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 769, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4288, 'They were stoned, they were sawn in two, were tempted, were slain with the sword. They wandered about in sheepskins and goatskins, being destitute, afflicted, tormented--', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 770, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4289, 'of whom the world was not worthy. They wandered in deserts and mountains, in dens and caves of the earth.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 771, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4290, 'And all these, having obtained a good testimony through faith, did not receive the promise,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 772, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4291, 'God having provided something better for us, that they should not be made perfect apart from us.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 773, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4292, 'Therefore we also, since we are surrounded by so great a cloud of witnesses, let us lay aside every weight, and the sin which so easily ensnares us, and let us run with endurance the race that is set before us,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 774, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4293, 'looking unto Jesus, the author and finisher of our faith, who for the joy that was set before Him endured the cross, despising the shame, and has sat down at the right hand of the throne of God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 775, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4294, 'For consider Him who endured such hostility from sinners against Himself, lest you become weary and discouraged in your souls.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 776, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4295, 'You have not yet resisted to bloodshed, striving against sin.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 777, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4296, 'And you have forgotten the exhortation which speaks to you as to sons: \"My son, do not despise the chastening of the Lord, Nor be discouraged when you are rebuked by Him;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 778, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4297, 'For whom the Lord loves He chastens, And scourges every son whom He receives.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 779, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4298, 'If you endure chastening, God deals with you as with sons; for what son is there whom a father does not chasten?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 780, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4299, 'But if you are without chastening, of which all have become partakers, then you are illegitimate and not sons.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 781, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4300, 'Furthermore, we have had human fathers who corrected us, and we paid them respect. Shall we not much more readily be in subjection to the Father of spirits and live?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 782, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4301, 'For they indeed for a few days chastened us as seemed best to them, but He for our profit, that we may be partakers of His holiness.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 783, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4302, 'Now no chastening seems to be joyful for the present, but painful; nevertheless, afterward it yields the peaceable fruit of righteousness to those who have been trained by it.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 784, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4303, 'Therefore strengthen the hands which hang down, and the feeble knees,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 785, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4304, 'and make straight paths for your feet, so that what is lame may not be dislocated, but rather be healed.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 786, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4305, 'Pursue peace with all people, and holiness, without which no one will see the Lord:', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 787, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4306, 'looking carefully lest anyone fall short of the grace of God; lest any root of bitterness springing up cause trouble, and by this many become defiled;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 788, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4307, 'lest there be any fornicator or profane person like Esau, who for one morsel of food sold his birthright.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 789, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4308, 'For you know that afterward, when he wanted to inherit the blessing, he was rejected, for he found no place for repentance, though he sought it diligently with tears.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 790, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4309, 'For you have not come to the mountain that may be touched and that burned with fire, and to blackness and darkness and tempest,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 791, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4310, 'and the sound of a trumpet and the voice of words, so that those who heard it begged that the word should not be spoken to them anymore.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 792, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4311, '(For they could not endure what was commanded: \"And if so much as a beast touches the mountain, it shall be stoned or shot with an arrow.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 793, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4312, 'And so terrifying was the sight that Moses said, \"I am exceedingly afraid and trembling.\")', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 794, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4313, 'But you have come to Mount Zion and to the city of the living God, the heavenly Jerusalem, to an innumerable company of angels,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 795, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4314, 'to the general assembly and church of the firstborn who are registered in heaven, to God the Judge of all, to the spirits of just men made perfect,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 796, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4315, 'to Jesus the Mediator of the new covenant, and to the blood of sprinkling that speaks better things than that of Abel.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 797, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4316, 'See that you do not refuse Him who speaks. For if they did not escape who refused Him who spoke on earth, much more shall we not escape if we turn away from Him who speaks from heaven,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 798, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4317, 'whose voice then shook the earth; but now He has promised, saying, \"Yet once more I shake not only the earth, but also heaven.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 799, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4318, 'Now this, \"Yet once more,\" indicates the removal of those things that are being shaken, as of things that are made, that the things which cannot be shaken may remain.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 800, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4319, 'Therefore, since we are receiving a kingdom which cannot be shaken, let us have grace, by which we may serve God acceptably with reverence and godly fear.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 801, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4320, 'For our God is a consuming fire.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:21:38', '2020-11-23 00:21:38', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 802, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4346, 'Peter, an apostle of Jesus Christ, To the pilgrims of the Dispersion in Pontus, Galatia, Cappadocia, Asia, and Bithynia,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 72, 776, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4347, 'elect according to the foreknowledge of God the Father, in sanctification of the Spirit, for obedience and sprinkling of the blood of Jesus Christ: Grace to you and peace be multiplied.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 949, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4348, 'Blessed be the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, who according to His abundant mercy has begotten us again to a living hope through the resurrection of Jesus Christ from the dead,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 950, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4349, 'to an inheritance incorruptible and undefiled and that does not fade away, reserved in heaven for you,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 951, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4350, 'who are kept by the power of God through faith for salvation ready to be revealed in the last time.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 952, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4351, 'In this you greatly rejoice, though now for a little while, if need be, you have been grieved by various trials,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 953, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4352, 'that the genuineness of your faith, being much more precious than gold that perishes, though it is tested by fire, may be found to praise, honor, and glory at the revelation of Jesus Christ,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 954, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4353, 'whom having not seen you love. Though now you do not see Him, yet believing, you rejoice with joy inexpressible and full of glory,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 955, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4354, 'receiving the end of your faith--the salvation of your souls.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 956, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4355, 'Of this salvation the prophets have inquired and searched carefully, who prophesied of the grace that would come to you,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 957, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4356, 'searching what, or what manner of time, the Spirit of Christ who was in them was indicating when He testified beforehand the sufferings of Christ and the glories that would follow.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 958, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4357, 'To them it was revealed that, not to themselves, but to us they were ministering the things which now have been reported to you through those who have preached the gospel to you by the Holy Spirit sent from heaven--things which angels desire to look into.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 959, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4358, 'Therefore gird up the loins of your mind, be sober, and rest your hope fully upon the grace that is to be brought to you at the revelation of Jesus Christ;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 960, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4359, 'as obedient children, not conforming yourselves to the former lusts, as in your ignorance;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 961, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4360, 'but as He who called you is holy, you also be holy in all your conduct,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 962, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4361, 'because it is written, \"Be holy, for I am holy.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 963, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4362, 'And if you call on the Father, who without partiality judges according to each one\'s work, conduct yourselves throughout the time of your stay here in fear;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 964, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4363, 'knowing that you were not redeemed with corruptible things, like silver or gold, from your aimless conduct received by tradition from your fathers,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 965, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4364, 'but with the precious blood of Christ, as of a lamb without blemish and without spot.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 966, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4365, 'He indeed was foreordained before the foundation of the world, but was manifest in these last times for you', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 967, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4366, 'who through Him believe in God, who raised Him from the dead and gave Him glory, so that your faith and hope are in God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 968, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4367, 'Since you have purified your souls in obeying the truth through the Spirit in sincere love of the brethren, love one another fervently with a pure heart,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 969, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4368, 'having been born again, not of corruptible seed but incorruptible, through the word of God which lives and abides forever,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 970, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4369, 'because \"All flesh is as grass, And all the glory of man as the flower of the grass. The grass withers, And its flower falls away,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 971, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4370, 'But the word of the Lord endures forever.\" Now this is the word which by the gospel was preached to you.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 972, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4371, 'Therefore, laying aside all malice, all deceit, hypocrisy, envy, and all evil speaking,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 973, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4372, 'as newborn babes, desire the pure milk of the word, that you may grow thereby,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 974, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4373, 'if indeed you have tasted that the Lord is gracious.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 975, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4374, 'Coming to Him as to a living stone, rejected indeed by men, but chosen by God and precious,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 976, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4375, 'you also, as living stones, are being built up a spiritual house, a holy priesthood, to offer up spiritual sacrifices acceptable to God through Jesus Christ.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 977, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4376, 'Therefore it is also contained in the Scripture, \"Behold, I lay in Zion A chief cornerstone, elect, precious, And he who believes on Him will by no means be put to shame.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 978, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4377, 'Therefore, to you who believe, He is precious; but to those who are disobedient, \"The stone which the builders rejected Has become the chief cornerstone,\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 979, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4378, 'and \"A stone of stumbling And a rock of offense.\" They stumble, being disobedient to the word, to which they also were appointed.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 980, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4379, 'But you are a chosen generation, a royal priesthood, a holy nation, His own special people, that you may proclaim the praises of Him who called you out of darkness into His marvelous light;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 981, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4380, 'who once were not a people but are now the people of God, who had not obtained mercy but now have obtained mercy.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 982, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4381, 'Beloved, I beg you as sojourners and pilgrims, abstain from fleshly lusts which war against the soul,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 983, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4382, 'having your conduct honorable among the Gentiles, that when they speak against you as evildoers, they may, by your good works which they observe, glorify God in the day of visitation.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 984, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4383, 'Therefore submit yourselves to every ordinance of man for the Lord\'s sake, whether to the king as supreme,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 985, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4384, 'or to governors, as to those who are sent by him for the punishment of evildoers and for the praise of those who do good.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 986, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4385, 'For this is the will of God, that by doing good you may put to silence the ignorance of foolish men--', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 987, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4386, 'as free, yet not using liberty as a cloak for vice, but as bondservants of God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 988, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4387, 'Honor all people. Love the brotherhood. Fear God. Honor the king.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 989, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4388, 'Servants, be submissive to your masters with all fear, not only to the good and gentle, but also to the harsh.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 990, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4389, 'For this is commendable, if because of conscience toward God one endures grief, suffering wrongfully.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 991, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4390, 'For what credit is it if, when you are beaten for your faults, you take it patiently? But when you do good and suffer, if you take it patiently, this is commendable before God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 992, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4391, 'For to this you were called, because Christ also suffered for us, leaving us an example, that you should follow His steps:', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 993, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4392, '\"Who committed no sin, Nor was deceit found in His mouth\";', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 994, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4393, 'who, when He was reviled, did not revile in return; when He suffered, He did not threaten, but committed Himself to Him who judges righteously;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 995, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4394, 'who Himself bore our sins in His own body on the tree, that we, having died to sins, might live for righteousness--by whose stripes you were healed.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 996, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4395, 'For you were like sheep going astray, but have now returned to the Shepherd and Overseer of your souls.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 997, NULL, NULL, 1);
INSERT INTO `Questions` (`QuestionID`, `Question`, `Answer`, `NumberPoints`, `DateCreated`, `DateModified`, `Type`, `CommentaryStartPage`, `CommentaryEndPage`, `IsDeleted`, `CreatorID`, `LastEditedByID`, `StartVerseID`, `EndVerseID`, `CommentaryID`, `LanguageID`) VALUES
(4396, 'Wives, likewise, be submissive to your own husbands, that even if some do not obey the word, they, without a word, may be won by the conduct of their wives,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 998, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4397, 'when they observe your chaste conduct accompanied by fear.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 999, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4398, 'Do not let your adornment be merely outward--arranging the hair, wearing gold, or putting on fine apparel--', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1000, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4399, 'rather let it be the hidden person of the heart, with the incorruptible beauty of a gentle and quiet spirit, which is very precious in the sight of God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1001, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4400, 'For in this manner, in former times, the holy women who trusted in God also adorned themselves, being submissive to their own husbands,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1002, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4401, 'as Sarah obeyed Abraham, calling him lord, whose daughters you are if you do good and are not afraid with any terror.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1003, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4402, 'Husbands, likewise, dwell with them with understanding, giving honor to the wife, as to the weaker vessel, and as being heirs together of the grace of life, that your prayers may not be hindered.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1004, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4403, 'Finally, all of you be of one mind, having compassion for one another; love as brothers, be tenderhearted, be courteous;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1005, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4404, 'not returning evil for evil or reviling for reviling, but on the contrary blessing, knowing that you were called to this, that you may inherit a blessing.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1006, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4405, 'For \"He who would love life And see good days, Let him refrain his tongue from evil, And his lips from speaking deceit.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1007, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4406, 'Let him turn away from evil and do good; Let him seek peace and pursue it.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1008, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4407, 'For the eyes of the Lord are on the righteous, And His ears are open to their prayers; But the face of the Lord is against those who do evil.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1009, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4408, 'And who is he who will harm you if you become followers of what is good?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1010, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4409, 'But even if you should suffer for righteousness\' sake, you are blessed. \"And do not be afraid of their threats, nor be troubled.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1011, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4410, 'But sanctify the Lord God in your hearts, and always be ready to give a defense to everyone who asks you a reason for the hope that is in you, with meekness and fear;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1012, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4411, 'having a good conscience, that when they defame you as evildoers, those who revile your good conduct in Christ may be ashamed.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1013, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4412, 'For it is better, if it is the will of God, to suffer for doing good than for doing evil.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1014, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4413, 'For Christ also suffered once for sins, the just for the unjust, that He might bring us to God, being put to death in the flesh but made alive by the Spirit,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1015, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4414, 'by whom also He went and preached to the spirits in prison,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1016, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4415, 'who formerly were disobedient, when once the Divine longsuffering waited in the days of Noah, while the ark was being prepared, in which a few, that is, eight souls, were saved through water.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1017, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4416, 'There is also an antitype which now saves us--baptism (not the removal of the filth of the flesh, but the answer of a good conscience toward God), through the resurrection of Jesus Christ,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1018, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4417, 'who has gone into heaven and is at the right hand of God, angels and authorities and powers having been made subject to Him.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1019, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4418, 'Therefore, since Christ suffered for us in the flesh, arm yourselves also with the same mind, for he who has suffered in the flesh has ceased from sin,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1020, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4419, 'that he no longer should live the rest of his time in the flesh for the lusts of men, but for the will of God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1021, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4420, 'For we have spent enough of our past lifetime in doing the will of the Gentiles--when we walked in lewdness, lusts, drunkenness, revelries, drinking parties, and abominable idolatries.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1022, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4421, 'In regard to these, they think it strange that you do not run with them in the same flood of dissipation, speaking evil of you.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1023, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4422, 'They will give an account to Him who is ready to judge the living and the dead.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1024, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4423, 'For this reason the gospel was preached also to those who are dead, that they might be judged according to men in the flesh, but live according to God in the spirit.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1025, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4424, 'But the end of all things is at hand; therefore be serious and watchful in your prayers.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1026, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4425, 'And above all things have fervent love for one another, for \"love will cover a multitude of sins.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1027, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4426, 'Be hospitable to one another without grumbling.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1028, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4427, 'As each one has received a gift, minister it to one another, as good stewards of the manifold grace of God.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1029, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4428, 'If anyone speaks, let him speak as the oracles of God. If anyone ministers, let him do it as with the ability which God supplies, that in all things God may be glorified through Jesus Christ, to whom belong the glory and the dominion forever and ever. Amen.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1030, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4429, 'Beloved, do not think it strange concerning the fiery trial which is to try you, as though some strange thing happened to you;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1031, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4430, 'but rejoice to the extent that you partake of Christ\'s sufferings, that when His glory is revealed, you may also be glad with exceeding joy.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1032, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4431, 'If you are reproached for the name of Christ, blessed are you, for the Spirit of glory and of God rests upon you. On their part He is blasphemed, but on your part He is glorified.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1033, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4432, 'But let none of you suffer as a murderer, a thief, an evildoer, or as a busybody in other people\'s matters.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1034, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4433, 'Yet if anyone suffers as a Christian, let him not be ashamed, but let him glorify God in this matter.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1035, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4434, 'For the time has come for judgment to begin at the house of God; and if it begins with us first, what will be the end of those who do not obey the gospel of God?', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1036, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4435, 'Now \"If the righteous one is scarcely saved, Where will the ungodly and the sinner appear?\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1037, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4436, 'Therefore let those who suffer according to the will of God commit their souls to Him in doing good, as to a faithful Creator.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:23', '2020-11-23 00:24:23', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1038, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4451, 'Simon Peter, a bondservant and apostle of Jesus Christ, To those who have obtained like precious faith with us by the righteousness of our God and Savior Jesus Christ:', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1053, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4452, 'Grace and peace be multiplied to you in the knowledge of God and of Jesus our Lord,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1054, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4453, 'as His divine power has given to us all things that pertain to life and godliness, through the knowledge of Him who called us by glory and virtue,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1055, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4454, 'by which have been given to us exceedingly great and precious promises, that through these you may be partakers of the divine nature, having escaped the corruption that is in the world through lust.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1056, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4455, 'But also for this very reason, giving all diligence, add to your faith virtue, to virtue knowledge,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1057, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4456, 'to knowledge self-control, to self-control perseverance, to perseverance godliness,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1058, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4457, 'to godliness brotherly kindness, and to brotherly kindness love.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1059, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4458, 'For if these things are yours and abound, you will be neither barren nor unfruitful in the knowledge of our Lord Jesus Christ.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1060, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4459, 'For he who lacks these things is shortsighted, even to blindness, and has forgotten that he was cleansed from his old sins.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1061, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4460, 'Therefore, brethren, be even more diligent to make your call and election sure, for if you do these things you will never stumble;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1062, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4461, 'for so an entrance will be supplied to you abundantly into the everlasting kingdom of our Lord and Savior Jesus Christ.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1063, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4462, 'For this reason I will not be negligent to remind you always of these things, though you know and are established in the present truth.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1064, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4463, 'Yes, I think it is right, as long as I am in this tent, to stir you up by reminding you,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1065, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4464, 'knowing that shortly I must put off my tent, just as our Lord Jesus Christ showed me.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1066, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4465, 'Moreover I will be careful to ensure that you always have a reminder of these things after my decease.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1067, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4466, 'For we did not follow cunningly devised fables when we made known to you the power and coming of our Lord Jesus Christ, but were eyewitnesses of His majesty.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1068, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4467, 'For He received from God the Father honor and glory when such a voice came to Him from the Excellent Glory: \"This is My beloved Son, in whom I am well pleased.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1069, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4468, 'And we heard this voice which came from heaven when we were with Him on the holy mountain.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1070, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4469, 'And so we have the prophetic word confirmed, which you do well to heed as a light that shines in a dark place, until the day dawns and the morning star rises in your hearts;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1071, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4470, 'knowing this first, that no prophecy of Scripture is of any private interpretation,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1072, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4471, 'for prophecy never came by the will of man, but holy men of God spoke as they were moved by the Holy Spirit.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1073, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4472, 'But there were also false prophets among the people, even as there will be false teachers among you, who will secretly bring in destructive heresies, even denying the Lord who bought them, and bring on themselves swift destruction.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1074, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4473, 'And many will follow their destructive ways, because of whom the way of truth will be blasphemed.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1075, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4474, 'By covetousness they will exploit you with deceptive words; for a long time their judgment has not been idle, and their destruction does not slumber.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1076, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4475, 'For if God did not spare the angels who sinned, but cast them down to hell and delivered them into chains of darkness, to be reserved for judgment;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1077, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4476, 'and did not spare the ancient world, but saved Noah, one of eight people, a preacher of righteousness, bringing in the flood on the world of the ungodly;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1078, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4477, 'and turning the cities of Sodom and Gomorrah into ashes, condemned them to destruction, making them an example to those who afterward would live ungodly;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1079, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4478, 'and delivered righteous Lot, who was oppressed by the filthy conduct of the wicked', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1080, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4479, '(for that righteous man, dwelling among them, tormented his righteous soul from day to day by seeing and hearing their lawless deeds)--', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1081, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4480, 'then the Lord knows how to deliver the godly out of temptations and to reserve the unjust under punishment for the day of judgment,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1082, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4481, 'and especially those who walk according to the flesh in the lust of uncleanness and despise authority. They are presumptuous, self-willed. They are not afraid to speak evil of dignitaries,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1083, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4482, 'whereas angels, who are greater in power and might, do not bring a reviling accusation against them before the Lord.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1084, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4483, 'But these, like natural brute beasts made to be caught and destroyed, speak evil of the things they do not understand, and will utterly perish in their own corruption,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1085, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4484, 'and will receive the wages of unrighteousness, as those who count it pleasure to carouse in the daytime. They are spots and blemishes, carousing in their own deceptions while they feast with you,', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1086, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4485, 'having eyes full of adultery and that cannot cease from sin, enticing unstable souls. They have a heart trained in covetous practices, and are accursed children.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1087, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4486, 'They have forsaken the right way and gone astray, following the way of Balaam the son of Beor, who loved the wages of unrighteousness;', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1088, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4487, 'but he was rebuked for his iniquity: a dumb donkey speaking with a man\'s voice restrained the madness of the prophet.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1089, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4488, 'These are wells without water, clouds carried by a tempest, for whom is reserved the blackness of darkness forever.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1090, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4489, 'For when they speak great swelling words of emptiness, they allure through the lusts of the flesh, through lewdness, the ones who have actually escaped from those who live in error.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1091, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4490, 'While they promise them liberty, they themselves are slaves of corruption; for by whom a person is overcome, by him also he is brought into bondage.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1092, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4491, 'For if, after they have escaped the pollutions of the world through the knowledge of the Lord and Savior Jesus Christ, they are again entangled in them and overcome, the latter end is worse for them than the beginning.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1093, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4492, 'For it would have been better for them not to have known the way of righteousness, than having known it, to turn from the holy commandment delivered to them.', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1094, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4493, 'But it has happened to them according to the true proverb: \"A dog returns to his own vomit,\" and, \"a sow, having washed, to her wallowing in the mire.\"', '', 1, '2020-11-23 00:24:26', '2020-11-23 00:24:26', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1095, NULL, NULL, 1),
