(9043, 'who said, \"The Sabbath was made for man, and not man for the Sabbath\"?  Be specific.', 'The Creator Himself', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9044, 'what did the Creator Himself say?', '\"The Sabbath was made for man, and not man for the Sabbath.\"', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9045, 'what two things have become special objects of Satan\'s attacks?', '(1) The Sabbath and (2) the home', 2, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9046, 'who has taken the Sabbath and the home as special objects of his attacks?', 'Satan', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9047, 'the relationship of mother-in-law to daughter-in-law is a subject of what to many people?', 'Amusement', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9048, 'what relationship of who to whom is a subject of amusement to many?', 'Mother-in-law to daughter-in-law', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9049, 'True or false: many people think of the way that mothers-in-law relate to daughters-in-law as a thing to joke about.', 'True.', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9050, 'was the relationship between Ruth and her mother-in-law, Naomi, a subject of amusement?', 'No', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9051, 'the relationship between which daughter-in-law and mother-in-law was not a matter for joking?', 'Ruth and Naomi', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9052, 'how long did Naomi sojourn [live] in the land of Moab?', '10 years', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9053, 'who in Naomi\'s family had died?', '(1) Her husband and (2) two sons', 2, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9054, 'after 10 years in Moab, Naomi learned that what prevailed in the land of Judah?', 'A condition of plenty', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9055, 'where did a condition of plenty prevail after Naomi had been in Moab for 10 years?', 'In the land of Judah', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9056, 'what two things did Naomi do after she had sojourned in Moab for 10 years?', '(1) Learned that a condition of plenty prevailed in the land of Judah and (2) decided to return', 2, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9057, 'what did Naomi decide to do when she learned that a condition of plenty prevailed in the land of Judah?', 'Return', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9058, 'what did Ruth break to accompany Naomi back to Judah?', 'All ties of home and kindred', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9059, 'Ruth broke all ties of what to accompany Naomi back to Judah?', '(1) Home and (2) kindred', 2, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9060, 'Ruth broke all ties of home and kindred to do what?', 'Accompany Naomi', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9061, 'with what virtue did Ruth break all ties of home and kindred to accompany Naomi?', 'Devotion', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9062, 'True or false: Ruth\'s devotion indicates that she was an admirable woman, and it also shows that Naomi was a wonderful mother-in-law.', 'True.', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9063, 'the devotion Ruth had says good things about which two women?', 'Ruth and Naomi', 2, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9064, 'what attribute of Ruth indicates not only her quality as a daughter-in-law but also Naomi\'s excellence as a mother in law?', 'Her devotion', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9065, 'what three things did Ruth do upon taking a last look at her homeland and pledging herself to Naomi?', 'She (1) entered a strange land, (2) united with God\'s true people and (3) became a worshiper of the God of heaven.', 3, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9066, 'what was Ruth\'s impassioned outburst to Naomi as she entered the land of Israel?', '``Thy people shall be my people, and thy God my God.\'\'', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9067, 'with what two things did Ruth enter a strange land?', '(1) With a last look at the fertile fields of her homeland, Moab, and (2) with an impassioned outburst to Naomi', 2, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9068, 'how are the fields of Moab described?', 'Fertile', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9069, 'what resulted in Ruth becoming the progenitor of David, Solomon, Zerubbabel and the Messiah?', 'Her devotion to her mother-in-law', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9070, 'Ruth\'s devotion to her mother-in-law resulted in her becoming the progenitor [ancestor] of which four men?', '(1) David, (2) Solomon, (3) Zerubbabel and (4) the Messiah', 4, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9071, 'how is David described?', 'The sweet psalmist of Israel', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9072, 'how is Solomon described?', 'The wisest of the sons of men', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9073, 'how is Zerubbabel described?', 'The later Moses', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9074, 'how is the Messiah described?', 'The son of David', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9075, 'the story of Ruth is replete [filled] with superb examples of what?', '(1) faith, (2) piety, (3) humility, (4) industry and (5) loving-kindness', 5, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9076, 'in the story of Ruth, faith, piety, humility, industry and loving-kindness are revealed in what?', 'The ordinary occurances of life', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9077, 'what two things do we have in the story of Ruth?', '(1) A charming gem of Hebrew literature and (2) a significant comment on a part of the genealogy of Christ', 2, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9078, 'in the story of Ruth we have a charming gem of what?', 'Hebrew literature', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9079, 'in the story of Ruth we have a significant comment on a part of what?', 'The genealogy of Christ', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9080, 'the story of Ruth provides a significant comment on the genealogy of whom?', 'Christ', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9081, 'in the context of Hebrew literature, what does the commentator call the story of Ruth?', 'A charming gem', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9082, 'Israel should have been prepared by what to understand God\'s plan of salvation for individuals of all nations who would accept Him?', 'By a study of the narrative of Ruth', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9083, 'who should have been prepared by studying Ruth to understand God\'s plan to save people from all nations who would accept him?', 'Israel', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9084, 'what should a study of Ruth have prepared Israel to understand?', 'God\'s plan for the salvation of individuals of all nations who would accept Him as Ruth did', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9085, 'which individuals from all nations does God\'s plan for salvation encompass?', 'Those who would do as Ruth the Moabitess did -- accept the God whose character had been represented to them by His servants', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9086, 'what did Ruth the Moabitess do that put her in the group of individuals included in God\'s plan?', 'Accepted God', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9087, 'which God do those individuals accept who do as Ruth did?', 'The God whose character had been represented to them by His servants', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9088, 'by whom was God\'s character represented?', 'His servants', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9089, 'of what does God want many to become citizens?  Be specific.', 'The eternal kingdom of Christ', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9090, 'what effect does the transformation in character have on those transformed?', 'They are prepared individually to become citizens of the eternal kingdom of Christ.', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9091, 'True or false: God planned that a certain few individuals from other nations would be prepared to become citizens of Christ\'s kindom.', 'False.  His plan was that many would be thus transformed.', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9092, 'God planned that many would be transformed in what?', 'In character', 1, '2022-02-02 17:38:50', '2022-02-02 17:38:50', 'commentary-qna', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, 3, 1),
(9093, 'Now Solomon assembled the elders of Israel and all the heads of the tribes, the chief fathers of the children of Israel, to King Solomon in Jerusalem, that they might bring up the ark of the covenant of the Lord from the City of David, which is Zion.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1489, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9094, 'Therefore all the men of Israel assembled with King Solomon at the feast in the month of Ethanim, which is the seventh month.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1490, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9095, 'So all the elders of Israel came, and the priests took up the ark.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1491, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9096, 'Then they brought up the ark of the Lord, the tabernacle of meeting, and all the holy furnishings that were in the tabernacle. The priests and the Levites brought them up.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1492, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9097, 'Also King Solomon, and all the congregation of Israel who were assembled with him, were with him before the ark, sacrificing sheep and oxen that could not be counted or numbered for multitude.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1493, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9098, 'Then the priests brought in the ark of the covenant of the Lord to its place, into the inner sanctuary of the temple, to the Most Holy Place, under the wings of the cherubim.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1494, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9099, 'For the cherubim spread their two wings over the place of the ark, and the cherubim overshadowed the ark and its poles.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1495, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9100, 'The poles extended so that the ends of the poles could be seen from the holy place, in front of the inner sanctuary; but they could not be seen from outside. And they are there to this day.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1496, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9101, 'Nothing was in the ark except the two tablets of stone which Moses put there at Horeb, when the Lord made a covenant with the children of Israel, when they came out of the land of Egypt.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1497, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9102, 'And it came to pass, when the priests came out of the holy place, that the cloud filled the house of the Lord,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1498, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9103, 'so that the priests could not continue ministering because of the cloud; for the glory of the Lord filled the house of the Lord.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1499, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9104, 'Then Solomon spoke: \"The Lord said He would dwell in the dark cloud.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1500, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9105, 'I have surely built You an exalted house, And a place for You to dwell in forever.\"', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1501, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9106, 'Then the king turned around and blessed the whole assembly of Israel, while all the assembly of Israel was standing.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1502, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9107, 'And he said: \"Blessed be the Lord God of Israel, who spoke with His mouth to my father David, and with His hand has fulfilled it, saying,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1503, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9108, '\'Since the day that I brought My people Israel out of Egypt, I have chosen no city from any tribe of Israel in which to build a house, that My name might be there; but I chose David to be over My people Israel.\'', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1504, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9109, 'Now it was in the heart of my father David to build a temple for the name of the Lord God of Israel.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1505, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9110, 'But the Lord said to my father David, \'Whereas it was in your heart to build a temple for My name, you did well that it was in your heart.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1506, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9111, 'Nevertheless you shall not build the temple, but your son who will come from your body, he shall build the temple for My name.\'', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1507, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9112, 'So the Lord has fulfilled His word which He spoke; and I have filled the position of my father David, and sit on the throne of Israel, as the Lord promised; and I have built a temple for the name of the Lord God of Israel.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1508, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9113, 'And there I have made a place for the ark, in which is the covenant of the Lord which He made with our fathers, when He brought them out of the land of Egypt.\"', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1509, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9114, 'Then Solomon stood before the altar of the Lord in the presence of all the assembly of Israel, and spread out his hands toward heaven;', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1510, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9115, 'and he said: \" Lord God of Israel, there is no God in heaven above or on earth below like You, who keep Your covenant and mercy with Your servants who walk before You with all their hearts.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1511, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9116, 'You have kept what You promised Your servant David my father; You have both spoken with Your mouth and fulfilled it with Your hand, as it is this day.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1512, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9117, 'Therefore, Lord God of Israel, now keep what You promised Your servant David my father, saying, \'You shall not fail to have a man sit before Me on the throne of Israel, only if your sons take heed to their way, that they walk before Me as you have walked before Me.\'', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1513, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9118, 'And now I pray, O God of Israel, let Your word come true, which You have spoken to Your servant David my father.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1514, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9119, '\"But will God indeed dwell on the earth? Behold, heaven and the heaven of heavens cannot contain You. How much less this temple which I have built!', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1515, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9120, 'Yet regard the prayer of Your servant and his supplication, O Lord my God, and listen to the cry and the prayer which Your servant is praying before You today:', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1516, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9121, 'that Your eyes may be open toward this temple night and day, toward the place of which You said, \'My name shall be there,\' that You may hear the prayer which Your servant makes toward this place.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1517, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9122, 'And may You hear the supplication of Your servant and of Your people Israel, when they pray toward this place. Hear in heaven Your dwelling place; and when You hear, forgive.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1518, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9123, '\"When anyone sins against his neighbor, and is forced to take an oath, and comes and takes an oath before Your altar in this temple,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1519, NULL, NULL, 1);
INSERT INTO `Questions` (`QuestionID`, `Question`, `Answer`, `NumberPoints`, `DateCreated`, `DateModified`, `Type`, `CommentaryStartPage`, `CommentaryEndPage`, `IsDeleted`, `CreatorID`, `LastEditedByID`, `StartVerseID`, `EndVerseID`, `CommentaryID`, `LanguageID`) VALUES
(9124, 'then hear in heaven, and act, and judge Your servants, condemning the wicked, bringing his way on his head, and justifying the righteous by giving him according to his righteousness.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1520, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9125, '\"When Your people Israel are defeated before an enemy because they have sinned against You, and when they turn back to You and confess Your name, and pray and make supplication to You in this temple,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1521, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9126, 'then hear in heaven, and forgive the sin of Your people Israel, and bring them back to the land which You gave to their fathers.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1522, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9127, '\"When the heavens are shut up and there is no rain because they have sinned against You, when they pray toward this place and confess Your name, and turn from their sin because You afflict them,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1523, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9128, 'then hear in heaven, and forgive the sin of Your servants, Your people Israel, that You may teach them the good way in which they should walk; and send rain on Your land which You have given to Your people as an inheritance.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1524, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9129, '\"When there is famine in the land, pestilence or blight or mildew, locusts or grasshoppers; when their enemy besieges them in the land of their cities; whatever plague or whatever sickness there is;', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1525, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9130, 'whatever prayer, whatever supplication is made by anyone, or by all Your people Israel, when each one knows the plague of his own heart, and spreads out his hands toward this temple:', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1526, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9131, 'then hear in heaven Your dwelling place, and forgive, and act, and give to everyone according to all his ways, whose heart You know (for You alone know the hearts of all the sons of men),', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1527, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9132, 'that they may fear You all the days that they live in the land which You gave to our fathers.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1528, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9133, '\"Moreover, concerning a foreigner, who is not of Your people Israel, but has come from a far country for Your name\'s sake', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1529, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9134, '(for they will hear of Your great name and Your strong hand and Your outstretched arm), when he comes and prays toward this temple,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1530, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9135, 'hear in heaven Your dwelling place, and do according to all for which the foreigner calls to You, that all peoples of the earth may know Your name and fear You, as do Your people Israel, and that they may know that this temple which I have built is called by Your name.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1531, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9136, '\"When Your people go out to battle against their enemy, wherever You send them, and when they pray to the Lord toward the city which You have chosen and the temple which I have built for Your name,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1532, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9137, 'then hear in heaven their prayer and their supplication, and maintain their cause.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1533, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9138, '\"When they sin against You (for there is no one who does not sin), and You become angry with them and deliver them to the enemy, and they take them captive to the land of the enemy, far or near;', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1534, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9139, 'yet when they come to themselves in the land where they were carried captive, and repent, and make supplication to You in the land of those who took them captive, saying, \'We have sinned and done wrong, we have committed wickedness\';', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1535, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9140, 'and when they return to You with all their heart and with all their soul in the land of their enemies who led them away captive, and pray to You toward their land which You gave to their fathers, the city which You have chosen and the temple which I have built for Your name:', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1536, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9141, 'then hear in heaven Your dwelling place their prayer and their supplication, and maintain their cause,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1537, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9142, 'and forgive Your people who have sinned against You, and all their transgressions which they have transgressed against You; and grant them compassion before those who took them captive, that they may have compassion on them', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1538, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9143, '(for they are Your people and Your inheritance, whom You brought out of Egypt, out of the iron furnace),', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1539, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9144, 'that Your eyes may be open to the supplication of Your servant and the supplication of Your people Israel, to listen to them whenever they call to You.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1540, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9145, 'For You separated them from among all the peoples of the earth to be Your inheritance, as You spoke by Your servant Moses, when You brought our fathers out of Egypt, O Lord God.\"', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1541, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9146, 'And so it was, when Solomon had finished praying all this prayer and supplication to the Lord, that he arose from before the altar of the Lord, from kneeling on his knees with his hands spread up to heaven.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1542, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9147, 'Then he stood and blessed all the assembly of Israel with a loud voice, saying:', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1543, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9148, '\"Blessed be the Lord, who has given rest to His people Israel, according to all that He promised. There has not failed one word of all His good promise, which He promised through His servant Moses.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1544, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9149, 'May the Lord our God be with us, as He was with our fathers. May He not leave us nor forsake us,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1545, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9150, 'that He may incline our hearts to Himself, to walk in all His ways, and to keep His commandments and His statutes and His judgments, which He commanded our fathers.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1546, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9151, 'And may these words of mine, with which I have made supplication before the Lord, be near the Lord our God day and night, that He may maintain the cause of His servant and the cause of His people Israel, as each day may require,', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1547, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9152, 'that all the peoples of the earth may know that the Lord is God; there is no other.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1548, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9153, 'Let your heart therefore be loyal to the Lord our God, to walk in His statutes and keep His commandments, as at this day.\"', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1549, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9154, 'Then the king and all Israel with him offered sacrifices before the Lord.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1550, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9155, 'And Solomon offered a sacrifice of peace offerings, which he offered to the Lord, twenty-two thousand bulls and one hundred and twenty thousand sheep. So the king and all the children of Israel dedicated the house of the Lord.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1551, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9156, 'On the same day the king consecrated the middle of the court that was in front of the house of the Lord ; for there he offered burnt offerings, grain offerings, and the fat of the peace offerings, because the bronze altar that was before the Lord was too small to receive the burnt offerings, the grain offerings, and the fat of the peace offerings.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1552, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9157, 'At that time Solomon held a feast, and all Israel with him, a great assembly from the entrance of Hamath to the Brook of Egypt, before the Lord our God, seven days and seven more days - fourteen days.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1553, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9158, 'On the eighth day he sent the people away; and they blessed the king, and went to their tents joyful and glad of heart for all the good that the Lord had done for His servant David, and for Israel His people.', '', 1, '2022-02-21 10:03:14', '2022-02-21 10:03:14', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1554, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9159, 'So King Solomon was king over all Israel.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1348, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9160, 'And these were his officials: Azariah the son of Zadok, the priest;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1349, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9161, 'Elihoreph and Ahijah, the sons of Shisha, scribes; Jehoshaphat the son of Ahilud, the recorder;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1350, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9162, 'Benaiah the son of Jehoiada, over the army; Zadok and Abiathar, the priests;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1351, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9163, 'Azariah the son of Nathan, over the officers; Zabud the son of Nathan, a priest and the king\'s friend;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1352, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9164, 'Ahishar, over the household; and Adoniram the son of Abda, over the labor force.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1353, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9165, 'And Solomon had twelve governors over all Israel, who provided food for the king and his household; each one made provision for one month of the year.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1354, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9166, 'These are their names: Ben-Hur, in the mountains of Ephraim;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1355, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9167, 'Ben-Deker, in Makaz, Shaalbim, Beth Shemesh, and Elon Beth Hanan;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1356, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9168, 'Ben-Hesed, in Arubboth; to him belonged Sochoh and all the land of Hepher;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1357, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9169, 'Ben-Abinadab, in all the regions of Dor; he had Taphath the daughter of Solomon as wife;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1358, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9170, 'Baana the son of Ahilud, in Taanach, Megiddo, and all Beth Shean, which is beside Zaretan below Jezreel, from Beth Shean to Abel Meholah, as far as the other side of Jokneam;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1359, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9171, 'Ben-Geber, in Ramoth Gilead; to him belonged the towns of Jair the son of Manasseh, in Gilead; to him also belonged the region of Argob in Bashan - sixty large cities with walls and bronze gate-bars;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1360, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9172, 'Ahinadab the son of Iddo, in Mahanaim;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1361, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9173, 'Ahimaaz, in Naphtali; he also took Basemath the daughter of Solomon as wife;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1362, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9174, 'Baanah the son of Hushai, in Asher and Aloth;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1363, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9175, 'Jehoshaphat the son of Paruah, in Issachar;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1364, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9176, 'Shimei the son of Elah, in Benjamin;', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1365, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9177, 'Geber the son of Uri, in the land of Gilead, in the country of Sihon king of the Amorites, and of Og king of Bashan. He was the only governor who was in the land.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1366, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9178, 'Judah and Israel were as numerous as the sand by the sea in multitude, eating and drinking and rejoicing.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1367, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9179, 'So Solomon reigned over all kingdoms from the River to the land of the Philistines, as far as the border of Egypt. They brought tribute and served Solomon all the days of his life.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1368, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9180, 'Now Solomon\'s provision for one day was thirty kors of fine flour, sixty kors of meal,', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1369, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9181, 'ten fatted oxen, twenty oxen from the pastures, and one hundred sheep, besides deer, gazelles, roebucks, and fatted fowl.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1370, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9182, 'For he had dominion over all the region on this side of the River from Tiphsah even to Gaza, namely over all the kings on this side of the River; and he had peace on every side all around him.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1371, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9183, 'And Judah and Israel dwelt safely, each man under his vine and his fig tree, from Dan as far as Beersheba, all the days of Solomon.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1372, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9184, 'Solomon had forty thousand stalls of horses for his chariots, and twelve thousand horsemen.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1373, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9185, 'And these governors, each man in his month, provided food for King Solomon and for all who came to King Solomon\'s table. There was no lack in their supply.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1374, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9186, 'They also brought barley and straw to the proper place, for the horses and steeds, each man according to his charge.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1375, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9187, 'And God gave Solomon wisdom and exceedingly great understanding, and largeness of heart like the sand on the seashore.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1376, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9188, 'Thus Solomon\'s wisdom excelled the wisdom of all the men of the East and all the wisdom of Egypt.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1377, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9189, 'For he was wiser than all men -  than Ethan the Ezrahite, and Heman, Chalcol, and Darda, the sons of Mahol; and his fame was in all the surrounding nations.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1378, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9190, 'He spoke three thousand proverbs, and his songs were one thousand and five.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1379, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9191, 'Also he spoke of trees, from the cedar tree of Lebanon even to the hyssop that springs out of the wall; he spoke also of animals, of birds, of creeping things, and of fish.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1380, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9192, 'And men of all nations, from all the kings of the earth who had heard of his wisdom, came to hear the wisdom of Solomon.', '', 1, '2022-02-22 08:22:35', '2022-02-22 08:22:35', 'bible-qna-fill', NULL, NULL, 0, 3, 3, 1381, NULL, NULL, 1);
